thread.title: Alan Castell
thread.title_full: CEWE Photoworld reviewed by Alan Castell

author: Alan Castell
title: Alan Castell
text:
I very much enjoy the process of producing our holiday or annual pictures using the very excellent software.
The results when the book is returned are amazing.
There are so many ways in which the book can be made interesting as the software offers a huge number of choices and yet is very easy to use.
Great that the completed book can be delivered to chosen store too, as it is usually too large to fit through our letterbox.
